<title type="html"><![CDATA[10/14(Thu.) Haunted house &amp; Lend Money (Host: Shuman)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=549&amp;p=572#p572"><![CDATA[
Place:Zoom Meeting<br />Agenda:<br />07:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />07:05-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />07:40-8:00 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited, 2 mins / each member)<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2 discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation<br /><br />Let's join the Zoom meeting this Thursday at 07:00 pm<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... 09#success<br /><br />會議 ID:929 8726 6213<br />密碼:112233<br /><br /><br />Haunted house in southwestern Taiwan is now up for sale<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://chinapost.nownews.com/20201120-1848616">https://chinapost.nownews.com/20201120-1848616</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question<br />1.Would you mind to buy a haunted house or be a neighbor ?<br />2.Do you know where we can check a haunted house?<br />3.Have you ever felt uncomfortable when you stay in somewhere?<br />4.It seems no law to erase the haunted house, can you set up rules?<br />5.Do you believe in’’風水’’?<br /><br /><br />12 Reasons You Should Never Lend Money to Friends &amp; Family<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.moneycrashers.com/why-you-should-not-lend-money-to-friends-and-family/">https://www.moneycrashers.com/why-you-s ... nd-family/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question<br />1.A new phrase’’ ‘’family blackmails’’(親情勒索), Have you ever met similar situation?<br />2.Have you ever borrow money from friends or family?<br />3.Have you ever lend money from friends or family?<br />4.Should we become a guarantor if family member request?<br />5.How can we refuse family or friends asking for unreasonable demand while keeping good a relationship?<br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.因疫情關係，聚會方式改為線上遠距。<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=872">Shuman</a> — Thu Oct 07, 2021 9:00 pm</p><hr />
